metadata.name: The 1st Sign - Murmillo
metadata.description:
The 1st Sign - Murmillo

Born and raised on a small planet in the Aquator system inhabited by Amphibiotes (homo amphibious).

Since childhood, he was interested in any kind of transport, everything that can fly, ride or swim.

He constantly participated in races on jet aquamarans, often coming out of them as a winner.

As a teenager, he often traded in smuggling, criminal structures appreciated his skills as a pilot and generously paid for his work...
